summary: Ever get tiered of the same old harvest jars in mods? But have no way to fix the problem!!! Well here is your solution you have been waiting for. A brand new set of harvestable jars Ready for use in your mod... And no they look nothing like the plain jane ones your used to. They will give plenty of flare to your mod.
descriptionHtml:
I'm in the process of making a new mod and needed a few resources that just didn't exist as I started putting everything together. So instead of asking for someone else to make what I needed. I went ahead and made my own resource to use. I figured everone else was also in need of These new Harvest Jars. So I decided as I make my new resources I'd upload them for other people to enjoy as well...Â 

The Jars work just like the originals. When you harvest the item inside. It will dissapear just like if you took it or picked a plant in skyrim. All the correct nodes and collission have been given to these meshes as well. The Ingrediants within the meshes use basic skyrim objects. So any mod that changes your ingrediant textures will effect these as well, But the jars themselves have there own texture paths for the glass, top and bottom, bottom ring and top handle... So these should be pritty compatable with everything exept mods that change the regular games meshes as well as textures. Because the new textures might not look right on the old ingredients used in these meshes...

Enjoy and if you want something new just send me a message. More than happy to lend a hand.
My work and mods will always be free to use as long as credit is given and not uploaded anywhere else...
I wouldn't mind a thumbs up on my mods as well if you find there to your liking. They take a long time to make and I just like that little bit of satisfaction knowing others like my work. It helps keep us modders into modding for others...
author: Lykaios
